  <para style="mt1">ZEKARIA</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ũhoro wa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="ip">Gĩcunjĩ kĩa mbere (1–8) kĩa ibuku rĩĩrĩ kĩheanaga ũhoro wa ũrĩa Mũnabii Zekaria onirio nĩ Ngai cioneki inyanya iria ingĩateithirie andũ kũhooya gũtooria mathĩĩna marĩa maarĩ namo.</para>
  <para style="ip">Mũthenya ũmwe mũthamaki ũrĩa ũthuurĩtwo nĩ Ngai nĩagatuĩka wa gwathana Jerusalemu, nao andũ-a-Ndũrĩrĩ matuĩke a kũgarũrũkĩra Ngai, matuĩke andũ ake. No ihinda-inĩ rĩu Ngai nĩathuurĩte Zerubabeli atuĩke barũthi, nake Joshua atuĩke mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai.</para>
  <para style="ip">Gĩcunjĩ-inĩ gĩa keerĩ (9–11) Ngai nĩeranĩire iherithia kũrĩ mabũrũri marĩa maariganĩtie na Juda, o hamwe na atongoria a Juda arĩa mataarĩ ehokeku.</para>
  <para style="ip">Gĩcunjĩ-inĩ gĩa gatatũ (12–14), Ngai nĩaheire Zekaria ndũmĩrĩri ĩkoniĩ ihinda rĩa mũthia.</para>
  <para style="iot">Mwandĩki</para>
  <para style="im">Ibuku rĩĩrĩ rĩandĩkirwo nĩ Zekaria.</para>
  <para style="iot">Ũrĩa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ Rĩgayanĩtio</para>
  <para style="io1">· Gũtaarĩria ibuku rĩothe <char style="ior"><ref loc="ZEC 1:1-6">1:1-6</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Cioneki inyanya cia ũtukũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="ZEC 1:1-6:8">1:1–6:8</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Joshua gwĩkĩrwo tanji ya mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai <char style="ior"><ref loc="ZEC 6:9-15">6:9-15</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Thĩĩna wa kwĩhinga, na kĩĩranĩro kĩrĩa gĩgooka <char style="ior"><ref loc="ZEC 7:1-8:23">7:1–8:23</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Kĩĩranĩro kĩnene kĩa Mesia, na ũtongoria wa thirikari ya Ngai <char style="ior"><ref loc="ZEC 9:1-14:21">9:1–14:21</ref></char>.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Isiraeli Gwĩtwo Macookerere Jehova</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZR 4:24">Ezar 4:24</ref>; <ref loc="NEH 12:4">Neh 12:4</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, mweri wa ĩnana wa mwaka wa keerĩ wa ũthamaki wa Dario, ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova nĩyakinyĩire mũnabii Zekaria, mũrũ wa Berekia, mũrũ wa Ido, akĩĩrwo atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Jehova nĩarakaririo mũno nĩ maithe manyu ma tene. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAL 3:7">Mal 3:7</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 4:8">Jak 4:8</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ĩra andũ atĩrĩ, Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: ‘Njookererai, nĩguo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga, na niĩ nĩngũmũcookerera,’ ũguo nĩguo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 6:17">Jer 6:17</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 106:6">Thab 106:6</ref></char></note>Mũtikahaane ta maithe manyu ma tene arĩa maahunjagĩrio nĩ anabii a tene, makeerwo atĩrĩ: Ũũ nĩguo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga: ‘Garũrũkai mũtige mĩthiĩre yanyu mĩũru o na mĩtugo yanyu mĩũru.’ No makĩaga kũnjigua kana kũrũmbũiya uuge wakwa, nĩguo Jehova ekuuga. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Maithe manyu ma tene makĩrĩ kũ rĩu? Nao anabii-rĩ, nĩmatũũraga nginya tene? <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 44:26">Isa 44:26</ref>; <ref loc="LAM 2:17">Maca 2:17</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, githĩ ndũmĩrĩri yakwa na irĩra ciakwa cia kũrũmĩrĩrwo, iria ndaathĩte ndungata ciakwa cia anabii itiahingĩirio maithe manyu ma tene?</para>
  <para style="p">“Hĩndĩ ĩyo makĩĩrira makiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe atwĩkĩte kũringana na ũrĩa mĩthiĩre na mĩtugo iitũ ĩtariĩ, o ta ũrĩa aatuĩte nĩegwĩka.’ ”</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũndũ ũrĩa warĩ Mĩtĩ-inĩ ya Mĩhandathi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Mũthenya wa mĩrongo ĩĩrĩ na ĩna wa mweri wa ikũmi na ũmwe, mweri ũcio wa Shebati, mwaka-inĩ wa keerĩ wa ũthamaki wa Dario, ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova nĩyakinyĩire mũnabii Zekaria, mũrũ wa Berekia, mũrũ wa Ido.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="REV 6:4">Kũg 6:4</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 6:2-7">Zek 6:2-7</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩndonire kĩoneki ũtukũ, na rĩrĩ, mbere yakwa ngĩona mũndũ wahaicĩte mbarathi ndune! Mũndũ ũcio aarũgamĩte mĩtĩ-inĩ ya mĩhandathi yarĩ handũ mũkuru-inĩ. Thuutha wake nĩ haarĩ mbarathi ĩmwe ndune, na ingĩ cia gĩĩtĩĩri na ingĩ njerũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEC 4:1">Zek 4:1</ref>, <ref loc="ZEC 4:4-5">4-5</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 7:16">Dan 7:16</ref></char>
    </note>Na niĩ ngĩũria atĩrĩ, “Mwathi wakwa, ici nacio nĩ cia kĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Mũraika ũcio waaragia na niĩ akĩnjookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩngũkwĩra nĩ cia kĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nake mũndũ ũcio warũngiĩ mĩtĩ-inĩ ya mĩhandathi akĩndaarĩria akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Aya nĩo Jehova atũmĩte mathiĩ thĩ yothe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 14:7">Isa 14:7</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 16:7">Kĩam 16:7</ref></char>
    </note>Nao magĩcookia ũhoro kũrĩ mũraika wa Jehova, ũrĩa warũngiĩ mĩtĩ-inĩ ya mĩhandathi, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Nĩtũthiĩte thĩ yothe na tũkoona atĩ thĩ nĩĩhooreire na ĩrĩ na thayũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 6:3">Thab 6:3</ref>; <ref loc="JER 40:5">Jer 40:5</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ mũraika ũcio wa Jehova akĩũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ nginya rĩ, Wee Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe, ũkwaga kũiguĩra Jerusalemu na matũũra ma Juda tha, marĩa ũkoretwo ũrakarĩire mĩaka mĩrongo mũgwanja?” <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 15:11">Ayub 15:11</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 4:1">Zek 4:1</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Jehova agĩkĩarĩria mũraika ũcio twaragia nake na ciugo njega na cia kũhoorerania.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nake mũraika ũcio wanjaragĩria akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Anĩrĩra ndũmĩrĩri ĩno: Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩnjiguaga ũiru nĩ ũndũ wa Jerusalemu na Zayuni, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CH 28:9">2Maũ 28:9</ref>; <ref loc="AMO 1:11">Amos 1:11</ref></char></note>no rĩrĩ, nĩndakarĩtio mũno nĩ ndũrĩrĩ iria ciĩiguaga irĩ ngitĩre. Ndaarakarĩire andũ akwa o hanini, no ndũrĩrĩ icio igĩkĩrĩrĩria kũmanyamaria.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEC 2:1-2">Zek 2:1-2</ref>; <ref loc="EZR 1:1">Ezar 1:1</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, Jehova ekuuga ũũ: ‘Nĩngacooka itũũra rĩa Jerusalemu ndĩrĩiguĩre tha, nayo nyũmba yakwa yakwo kuo rĩngĩ. Naruo rũrigi rũa gũthima nĩrũgatambũrũkio Jerusalemu,’ ũguo nĩguo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 40:1">Isa 40:1</ref>; <ref loc="EZR 9:9">Ezar 9:9</ref></char>
    </note>“Ningĩ ũthiĩ na mbere na kwanĩrĩra uuge atĩrĩ: Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ, ‘Matũũra makwa nĩmakaiyũrĩrĩra ũgaacĩru rĩngĩ, nake Jehova nĩakahooreria Zayuni rĩngĩ na ethuurĩre Jerusalemu.’ ”</para>
  <para style="s1">Hĩa Inya na Mabundi Mana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ningĩ ngĩtiira maitho, na rĩrĩ, mbere yakwa ngĩona hĩa inya! <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="AMO 6:13">Amos 6:13</ref></char></note>Ngĩũria mũraika ũcio wanjaragĩria atĩrĩ, “Ici nacio nĩ cia kĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake akĩnjookeria atĩrĩ, “Ici nĩcio hĩa iria ciaharaganirie Juda, na Isiraeli, na Jerusalemu.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:19 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Hĩa icio inya ciarĩ mabũrũri ma Ashuri, na Misiri, na Babuloni, na Perisia.</char></note></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nake Jehova agĩcooka akĩnyonia mabundi mana. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 75:10">Thab 75:10</ref></char></note>Na niĩ ngĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Aya-rĩ, marooka gwĩka atĩa?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake akĩnjookeria atĩrĩ, “Ici nĩcio hĩa iria ciaharaganirie Juda nĩguo gũtigacooke kuoneka mũndũ ũkwĩhaanda, no mabundi maya, mokĩte kũmamakia na magũithie hĩa icio cia ndũrĩrĩ, iria ciambararirie hĩa ciao igĩũkĩrĩra bũrũri wa Juda, nĩguo andũ akuo maharaganio.”</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mũndũ warĩ na Rũrigi rwa Gũthima</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ ngĩtiira maitho, na rĩrĩ, hau mbere yakwa ngĩona mũndũ wanyiitĩte rũrigi rũa gũthima na guoko gwake. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 40:3">Ezek 40:3</ref>; <ref loc="REV 21:15">Kũg 21:15</ref></char></note>Ngĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee-rĩ, wathiĩ kũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake akĩnjookeria atĩrĩ, “Ndathiĩ gũthima itũũra rĩa Jerusalemu, nĩguo menye wariĩ o na ũraihu warĩo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, mũraika ũcio wanjaragĩria agĩthiĩ, nake mũraika ũngĩ agĩũka kũmũtũnga, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 38:11">Ezek 38:11</ref>; <ref loc="JER 30:19">Jer 30:19</ref></char></note>akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Tengʼera wĩre mwanake ũcio atĩrĩ, ‘Jerusalemu rĩgaatuĩka itũũra inene rĩtarĩ thingo, nĩ ũndũ wa ũingĩ wa andũ na mahiũ marĩa magaakorwo kuo.’ <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 26:1">Isa 26:1</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 85:9">Thab 85:9</ref></char></note>Jehova ekuuga ũũ, ‘Niĩ mwene nĩ niĩ ngaatuĩka rũthingo rwa mwaki ndĩrĩthiũrũrũkĩrie, na nduĩke riiri thĩinĩ wa itũũra rĩu.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 17:21">Ezek 17:21</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 24:31">Math 24:31</ref></char>
    </note>Jehova ekuuga ũũ, “Ũkai, ũkai! Ũrai muume bũrũri wa mwena wa gathigathini, nĩgũkorwo ndĩmũharaganĩirie mĩena yothe ĩna ĩrĩa yumaga huho cia igũrũ,” ũguo nĩguo Jehova ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>“Ũka, wee Zayuni! Wĩthare, o wee ũtũũraga kwa Mwarĩ wa Babuloni!” <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 32:10">Gũcook 32:10</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga atĩrĩ, “Thuutha wa kũũhe gĩtĩĩo, akĩndũma ngahũũrane na ndũrĩrĩ iria ciatahĩte indo cianyu. Nĩgũkorwo ũrĩa wothe ũmũhutagia inyuĩ nĩ kĩũma kĩa riitho rĩa Ngai ahutagia. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 4:9">Zek 4:9</ref>; <ref loc="HAB 2:8">Hab 2:8</ref></char></note>Ti-itherũ nĩngambararia guoko gwakwa ndĩmookĩrĩre, nacio ngombo ciao itahe indo ciao. Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩguo mũkaamenya atĩ Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩwe ũndũmĩte.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEP 3:14">Zef 3:14</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 25:8">Thaam 25:8</ref></char>
    </note>“Wee Mwarĩ wa Zayuni-rĩ, anĩrĩra na ũkene, nĩgũkorwo nĩndĩrooka gũtũũra gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu,” ũguo nĩguo Jehova ekuuga. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 24:7">Jer 24:7</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 4:9">Zek 4:9</ref></char></note>“Mũthenya ũcio-rĩ, ndũrĩrĩ nyingĩ nĩikanyiitithanio na Jehova, na nĩmagatuĩka andũ akwa. Ngaatũũra gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu na nĩmũkamenya atĩ Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩwe ũndũmĩte kũrĩ inyuĩ.” <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 34:9">Thaam 34:9</ref>; <ref loc="JER 40:5">Jer 40:5</ref></char></note>Jehova nĩakagaya Juda gũtuĩke igai rĩake bũrũri-inĩ ũrĩa mũtheru, na nĩagethuurĩra Jerusalemu o rĩngĩ. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 14:14">Thaam 14:14</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 26:15">Gũcook 26:15</ref></char></note>Hoorerai harĩ Jehova inyuĩ kĩrĩndĩ gĩa thĩ tondũ nĩeyarahũrĩte kuuma gĩikaro-ini gĩake gĩtheru.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Nguo Theru cia Mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa Mũnene</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZR 2:2">Ezar 2:2</ref>; <ref loc="2SA 24:1">2Sam 24:1</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ akĩnyonia Joshua, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene, arũgamĩte mbere ya mũraika wa Jehova, nake Shaitani arũgamĩte mwena wake wa ũrĩo nĩguo amũcuuke. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 14:1">Isa 14:1</ref>; <ref loc="JUD 1:23">Jud 1:23</ref></char></note>Nake Jehova akĩĩra Shaitani atĩrĩ, “Jehova arogũkũũma, wee Shaitani! Jehova ũrĩa ũthuurĩte Jerusalemu arogũkũũma wee! Githĩ mũndũ ũyũ ti gĩcinga gĩtharĩtwo kuuma mwaki-inĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, Joshua eehumbĩte nguo irĩ gĩko hĩndĩ ĩyo aarũgamĩte mbere ya mũraika. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2SA 12:13">2Sam 12:13</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 41:42">Kĩam 41:42</ref></char></note>Mũraika ũcio akĩĩra arĩa maarũngiĩ mbere yake atĩrĩ, “Mũrutei nguo icio ciake irĩ na gĩko.”</para>
  <para style="p">Agĩcooka akĩĩra Joshua atĩrĩ, “Atĩrĩrĩ, nĩnjeheretie mehia maku, na nĩngũkũhumba nguo cia goro.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Ngĩcooka ngiuga atĩrĩ, “Muohei kĩremba gĩtheru mũtwe.” Nĩ ũndũ ũcio makĩmuoha kĩremba gĩtheru mũtwe, na makĩmũhumba nguo, mũraika wa Jehova arũgamĩte o hau.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Mũraika wa Jehova agĩatha Joshua, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 17:8-11">Gũcook 17:8-11</ref>; <ref loc="JER 15:19">Jer 15:19</ref></char></note>“Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ, ‘Ũngĩrũmĩrĩra mĩthiĩre yakwa na ũmenyagĩrĩre maũndũ marĩa nyendaga mekwo, nĩũgaathaga nyũmba yakwa, o na ũtuĩke mũrũgamĩrĩri wa nja ciayo, na ngwĩtĩkĩrie ũtuĩke ũmwe wa andũ aya marũngiĩ haha.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:46">Gũcook 28:46</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 4:2">Isa 4:2</ref></char>
    </note>“ ‘Ta thikĩrĩria, wee Joshua, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene, hamwe na athiritũ aku aya maikarĩte thĩ mbere yaku, o acio kĩmenyithia kĩa maũndũ marĩa magooka: Nĩngarehe ndungata yakwa, o we Rũhonge.’ <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 28:16">Isa 28:16</ref>; <ref loc="2SA 12:13">2Sam 12:13</ref></char></note>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ, ‘Atĩrĩrĩ, nĩnjigĩte ihiga mbere ya Joshua! Ihiga rĩu rĩrĩ na maitho mũgwanja, na nĩngakurura maandĩko igũrũ warĩo, na njeherie mehia ma bũrũri ũyũ na mũthenya ũmwe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 16:14">Ndar 16:14</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 4:4">Mik 4:4</ref></char>
    </note>“ ‘Mũthenya ũcio-rĩ, o mũndũ wanyu nĩageeta mũndũ wa itũũra rĩake maikare rungu rwa mũtĩ wake wa mũthabibũ na wa mũkũyũ,’ ” ũguo nĩguo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga.</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mũtĩ wa Thahabu wa Kũigĩrĩra Tawa na Mĩtĩ Ĩĩrĩ ya Mĩtamaiyũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DAN 8:18">Dan 8:18</ref>; <ref loc="JER 31:26">Jer 31:26</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo mũraika ũrĩa twaranagĩria nake akĩhũndũka, akĩnjarahũra, ta ũrĩa mũndũ aarahũragwo kuuma toro. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 25:31">Thaam 25:31</ref></char></note>Nake akĩnjũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kĩĩ ũroona?”</para>
  <para style="p">Na niĩ ngĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ndĩrona mũtĩ wa thahabu theri wa kũigĩrĩrwo tawa, ũrĩ na mbakũri igũrũ rĩaguo, na ũigĩrĩirwo matawa mũgwanja na mĩberethi mũgwanja ya gũtwara maguta matawa-inĩ macio. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 1:3">Thab 1:3</ref></char></note>Ningĩ harĩ na mĩtĩ ĩĩrĩ ya mĩtamaiyũ ĩriganĩtie naguo, ũmwe ũrĩ mwena wa ũrĩo wa mbakũri, na ũrĩa ũngĩ mwena wayo wa ũmotho.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ngĩũria mũraika ũrĩa twaranagĩria atĩrĩ, “Mwathi wakwa, ici nacio nĩ ndũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Nake akĩnjũũria atĩrĩ, “Wee-rĩ, ndũũĩ ici nĩ ndũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Na niĩ ngĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Aca, Mwathi wakwa, ndiũĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1SA 2:9">1Sam 2:9</ref>; <ref loc="HOS 1:7">Hos 1:7</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Ĩno nĩyo ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova kũrĩ Zerubabeli, nayo ĩkuuga ũũ: ‘Ti ũndũ wa hinya kana wa ũhoti, no nĩ ũndũ wa Roho wakwa,’ ũguo nĩguo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 51:25">Jer 51:25</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 118:22">Thab 118:22</ref></char>
    </note>“Wee kĩrĩma gĩkĩ kĩnene-rĩ, ũkĩrĩ ũ? Ũgaatuĩka kũndũ kwaraganu mbere ya Zerubabeli. Ningĩ nĩwe ũkaarehe ihiga rĩa kũrĩĩkia mwako o gũkĩanagĩrĩrwo atĩrĩ, ‘Ngai rĩrathime! Ngai rĩrathime!’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Ningĩ ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova ĩkĩnginyĩrĩra ngĩĩrwo atĩrĩ: <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZR 3:11">Ezar 3:11</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 6:12">Zek 6:12</ref></char></note>“Moko ma Zerubabeli nĩmo maakĩte mũthingi wa hekarũ ĩno, na moko make no mo makaamĩrĩkia. Hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩmũkamenya atĩ Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩwe ũndũmĩte kũrĩ inyuĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HAG 2:3">Hag 2:3</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 16:9">2Maũ 16:9</ref></char>
    </note>“Nũũ ũmenaga mũthenya wa kĩambĩrĩria kĩa maũndũ manini? Andũ nĩmagakena moona kabirũ karĩ guoko-inĩ gwa Zerubabeli. (Maya nĩmo maitho mũgwanja ma Jehova, marĩa moonaga thĩ yothe.)”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEC 4:3">Zek 4:3</ref>; <ref loc="REV 11:4">Kũg 11:4</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ ngĩũria mũraika ũcio atĩrĩ, “Mĩtamaiyũ ĩno ĩĩrĩ ĩrĩ mwena wa ũrĩo na wa ũmotho wa mũtĩ wa kũigĩrĩra tawa nĩ mĩtũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Ningĩ ngĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Honge ici igĩrĩ cia mĩtamaiyũ irũgamanĩte na mĩberethi ĩno ya thahabu iraita maguta mahaana ta thahabu nĩ ndũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nake agĩcookia atĩrĩ, “Wee-rĩ, ndũũĩ ici nĩ ndũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Na niĩ ngiuga atĩrĩ, “Aca, Mwathi wakwa, ndiũĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Aya eerĩ nĩo maitĩrĩirio maguta nĩguo matungatage Mwathani wa thĩ yothe.”</para>
  <chapter number="5" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ibuku rĩa Gĩkũnjo Rĩũmbũkĩte Rĩera-inĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 40:7">Thab 40:7</ref>; <ref loc="REV 5:1">Kũg 5:1</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ ngĩcooka ngĩtiira maitho, na rĩrĩ, hau mbere yakwa ngĩona ibuku-rĩa-gĩkũnjo rĩombũkaga rĩera-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>Nake akĩnjũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kĩĩ ũroona?”</para>
  <para style="p">Na niĩ ngĩmũcookeria atĩrĩ, “Ndĩrona ibuku-rĩa-gĩkũnjo rĩrombũka rĩera-inĩ, rĩrĩ na ũraihu wa mĩkono mĩrongo ĩĩrĩ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">nĩ ta mita 9</char></note> na wariĩ wa mĩkono ikũmi<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">nĩ ta mita inya na nuthu (4.5)</char></note>.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAL 3:9">Mal 3:9</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 24:6">Isa 24:6</ref></char>
    </note>Nake akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Gĩkĩ nĩ kĩrumi kĩrĩa gĩgũtambũrũka bũrũri wothe; nĩgũkorwo kũringana na ũrĩa mwena ũmwe warĩo wandĩkĩtwo, mũici o wothe no nginya agaathaamio, naguo mwena ũcio ũngĩ warĩo ũkandĩkwo atĩrĩ, ũrĩa wothe wĩhĩtaga na maheeni nĩagathaamio. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 14:34-35">Alaw 14:34-35</ref>; <ref loc="MAL 3:5">Mal 3:5</ref></char></note>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga atĩrĩ, ‘Nĩngatũma kĩrumi kĩu, nakĩo nĩgĩgatoonya nyũmba ya mũici na nyũmba ya ũrĩa wĩhĩtaga na maheeni akĩgwetaga rĩĩtwa rĩakwa. Gĩgaikara nyũmba yake na kĩmĩanange yothe, kĩanange mbaũ ciayo na mahiga mayo.’ ”</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũndũ-wa-nja arĩ thĩinĩ wa Gĩkabũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Ningĩ mũraika ũrĩa wanjaragĩria akiumĩra akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Tiira maitho wone nĩ kĩĩ gĩkĩ kĩroimĩra.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MIC 6:10">Mik 6:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ngĩmũũria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ kĩĩ gĩkĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">Nake akĩnjookeria atĩrĩ, “Nĩ gĩkabũ gĩa gũthima.” Agĩcooka akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩguo waganu wa andũ, ũrĩa ũrĩ bũrũri wothe.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nakĩo gĩkunĩko gĩa kĩgera gĩgĩkunũrwo, na rĩrĩ, hau thĩinĩ wa gĩkabũ ngĩona mũndũ-wa-nja waikarĩte thĩ ho. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MIC 6:11">Mik 6:11</ref></char></note>Nake akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩwe Nyawaganu,” nake akĩmũcookia thĩinĩ wa gĩkabũ na agĩgĩkunĩka na gĩkunĩko kĩu gĩa kĩgera.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 11:19">Alaw 11:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ngĩcooka ngĩtiira maitho, na rĩrĩ, hau mbere yakwa ngĩona andũ-a-nja eerĩ, mareretio nĩ rũhuho; tondũ maarĩ na mathagu ta ma njũũ, makĩoya gĩkabũ kĩu magĩgĩtwara rĩera-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Ngĩũria mũraika ũcio wanjaragĩria atĩrĩ, “Maratwara gĩkabũ kĩu kũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 10:10">Kĩam 10:10</ref>; <ref loc="JER 29:5">Jer 29:5</ref>, <ref loc="JER 29:28">28</ref></char>
    </note>Nake akĩnjookeria atĩrĩ, “Maragĩtwara bũrũri wa Babuloni magagĩakĩre nyũmba kuo. Yarĩka-rĩ, gĩkabũ kĩu makĩige kuo handũ hakĩo.”</para>
  <chapter number="6" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ngaari Inya cia Ita</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ningĩ ngĩtiira maitho rĩngĩ, na rĩrĩ, ngĩona ngaari inya cia ita igĩũka ciumĩte gatagatĩ ka irĩma igĩrĩ, irĩma icio ciarĩ cia gĩcango! <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="REV 6:5">Kũg 6:5</ref></char></note>Ngaari ya mbere yaguucĩtio nĩ mbarathi ndune, na ya keerĩ ĩkaguucio nĩ mbarathi njirũ, <verse number="3" style="v"/>na ya gatatũ ĩkaguucio nĩ mbarathi njerũ, nayo ya kana ĩkaguucio nĩ mbarathi cia marooro; ciothe ciarĩ mbarathi ciarĩ na hinya. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ngĩũria mũraika ũcio wanjaragĩria atĩrĩ, “Mwathi wakwa, ici nacio nĩ ndũũ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 24:31">Math 24:31</ref>; <ref loc="REV 7:1">Kũg 7:1</ref></char>
    </note>Nake mũraika ũcio akĩnjookeria atĩrĩ, “Maya nĩ maroho marĩa mana ma igũrũ, maroima harĩa marũgamaga mbere ya Mwathani wa thĩ yothe. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Ngaari ĩyo ĩguucĩtio nĩ mbarathi njirũ yerekeire bũrũri wa gathigathini, nayo ĩyo ĩguucĩtio nĩ mbarathi njerũ yerekeire bũrũri wa ithũĩro, nayo ĩyo ĩguucĩtio nĩ mbarathi irĩ na maroro yerekeire bũrũri wa gũthini.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 43:6">Isa 43:6</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 1:8">Zek 1:8</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa mbarathi icio irĩ hinya cioimagarire-rĩ, nĩciageragia mũno ũrĩa ingĩthiĩ thĩ yothe. Nake agĩciĩra atĩrĩ, “Thiĩi mũcange thĩ yothe!” Nĩ ũndũ ũcio igĩthiĩ thĩ yothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 5:13">Ezek 5:13</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 1:10">Zek 1:10</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ agĩcooka akĩnjĩta akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Ta rora, icio cierekeire bũrũri wa gathigathini nĩitũmĩte Roho wakwa ũgĩe na ũhurũko kũu bũrũri wa gathigathini.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Thũmbĩ ya Joshua</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova nĩyanginyĩrire ngĩĩrwo atĩrĩ, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZR 7:14-16">Ezar 7:14-16</ref>; <ref loc="JER 28:6">Jer 28:6</ref></char></note>“Amũkĩra betha na thahabu kuuma kũrĩ andũ arĩa maatahĩtwo, na nĩo Helidai, na Tobija, na Jedaia, arĩa mokĩte kuuma Babuloni. Thiĩ o ũmũthĩ mũciĩ kwa Josia mũrũ wa Zefania. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CH 6:15">1Maũ 6:15</ref>; <ref loc="EZR 3:2">Ezar 3:2</ref></char></note>Oya betha na thahabu icio ũthondeke thũmbĩ, ũcooke ũmĩigĩrĩre mũtwe wa Joshua mũrũ wa Jehozadaki, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 4:2">Isa 4:2</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 4:6-9">Zek 4:6-9</ref></char></note>Mwĩre atĩ Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: ‘Ũyũ nĩwe mũndũ ũrĩa wĩtagwo Rũhonge, nake nĩakaruta honge arĩ handũ haake na ake hekarũ ya Jehova. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 110:4">Thab 110:4</ref></char></note>Ũcio nĩwe ũgaaka hekarũ ya Jehova, na nĩakahumbwo riiri, na nĩagaikarĩra gĩtĩ gĩake kĩa ũnene aathane. O na nĩagatungata arĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai aikarĩire gĩtĩ gĩake kĩa ũnene; na maũndũ macio meerĩ nĩmakaganĩrĩra wega.’ <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nayo thũmbĩ ĩyo ĩigwo thĩinĩ wa hekarũ ya Jehova, ĩrĩ kĩririkano kĩa Helidai, na Tobija, na Jedaia, na Heni mũrũ wa Zefania. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 60:10">Isa 60:10</ref>; <ref loc="JER 7:23">Jer 7:23</ref></char></note>Arĩa marĩ kũraya nĩmagooka gũteithia gwaka hekarũ ya Jehova, na inyuĩ nĩmũkamenya atĩ Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩwe ũndũmĩte kũrĩ inyuĩ. Ũndũ ũyũ nĩũgekĩka mũngĩgaathĩkĩra Jehova Ngai wanyu mũrĩ na kĩyo.”</para>
  <chapter number="7" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Cariai Kĩhooto na Tha, ti Kwĩhinga Kũrĩa Irio</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZR 5:1">Ezar 5:1</ref>; <ref loc="NEH 1:1">Neh 1:1</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, mwaka-inĩ wa ĩna wa ũthamaki wa Dario, ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova nĩyakinyĩire Zekaria, mũthenya wa kana wa mweri wa kenda, na nĩguo mweri wa Kiselevu. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 26:19">Jer 26:19</ref>; <ref loc="HAG 2:10-14">Hag 2:10-14</ref></char></note>Andũ a Betheli nĩmatũmĩte Sharezeru na Regemu-Meleku hamwe na andũ ao magathaithe Jehova <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2KI 25:9">2Ath 25:9</ref></char></note>na kũũria athĩnjĩri-Ngai a nyũmba ya Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe na anabii atĩrĩ, “Nĩnjagĩrĩirwo nĩ gũcakaya na kwĩhinga kũrĩa irio mweri wa gatano, ta ũrĩa njĩkĩte mĩaka mĩingĩ?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ningĩ ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩyanginyĩrire akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 58:5">Isa 58:5</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 9:2">Dan 9:2</ref></char></note>“Ũria andũ othe a bũrũri o na athĩnjĩri-Ngai atĩrĩ, ‘Rĩrĩa mwehingaga kũrĩa irio mũgĩcakayaga mweri-inĩ wa gatano na wa mũgwanja ihinda rĩa mĩaka mĩrongo mũgwanja-rĩ, ti-itherũ mwehingaga kũrĩa irio nĩ ũndũ wakwa? <verse number="6" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩa mwarĩĩaga na mũkanyua-rĩ, githĩ mũtiarĩĩaga ndĩa ĩyo nĩ ũndũ wa inyuĩ ene? <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 22:21">Jer 22:21</ref></char></note>Githĩ ici ticio ciugo cia Jehova iria cianĩrĩirwo igereire harĩ anabii a tene, rĩrĩa Jerusalemu na matũũra marĩa maarĩthiũrũrũkĩirie maarĩ na ũhurũko na makaagaacĩra, nakuo Negevu na hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia irĩma cia mwena wa ithũĩro nĩ gwatũũragwo nĩ andũ?’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova nĩyakinyĩire Zekaria o rĩngĩ akĩĩrwo atĩrĩ: <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 22:1">Gũcook 22:1</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 8:16">Zek 8:16</ref></char></note>“Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: ‘Tuagai ciira na kĩhooto; iguanagĩrai tha na mũcaayanagĩre mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 49:11">Jer 49:11</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 25:17">Alaw 25:17</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 6:8">Mik 6:8</ref></char></note>Mũtikanahinyĩrĩrie mũtumia wa ndigwa kana mwana wa ngoriai, kana mũndũ wa kũngĩ, kana mũthĩĩni. Mũtikaneciiranĩrie ũũru ngoro-inĩ cianyu.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 11:10">Jer 11:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“No nĩmaregire kũigua; makĩngʼathia, na makĩhũgũka na magĩthinga matũ mao. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NEH 9:29">Neh 9:29</ref>; <ref loc="JER 42:21">Jer 42:21</ref></char></note>Nao makĩũmia ngoro ciao o ta ihiga rĩa nyaigĩ, na matingĩathikĩrĩirie watho kana ndũmĩrĩri ĩrĩa Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe aamatũmĩire na Roho wake, aarĩtie na tũnua twa anabii a tene. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe akĩrakara mũno.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 1:15">Isa 1:15</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 1:28">Thim 1:28</ref></char>
    </note>“Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga atĩrĩ, ‘Rĩrĩa ndeetanire, matiathikĩrĩirie; nĩ ũndũ ũcio rĩrĩa nao maanjĩtire, ndiamathikĩrĩirie. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 4:27">Gũcook 4:27</ref>; <ref loc="JER 44:6">Jer 44:6</ref></char></note>Nĩndamaharaganirie na kĩhuhũkanio kĩnene ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ ciothe, magĩtũũra kuo marĩ ageni. Bũrũri wao watigirwo ũkirĩte ihooru, na nĩ ũndũ ũcio gũkĩaga mũndũ ũngĩũtuĩkania kana acooke kuo. Ũguo nĩguo maatũmire bũrũri ũcio mwega ũkire ihooru.’ ”</para>
  <chapter number="8" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jehova Kwĩranĩra Kũrathima Jerusalemu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>O rĩngĩ ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩyanginyĩrire, ngĩĩrwo atĩrĩ: <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOL 2:18">Joel 2:18</ref></char></note>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: “Nĩnjiguaga ũiru mũno nĩ ũndũ wa Zayuni; nĩndĩracinwo nĩ ũiru nĩ ũndũ wake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 52:8">Isa 52:8</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 15:2">Thab 15:2</ref></char>
    </note>Jehova ekuuga ũũ: “Nĩngacooka Zayuni, ndũũre Jerusalemu. Hĩndĩ ĩyo itũũra rĩa Jerusalemu rĩgeetagwo Itũũra Inene rĩa Ũhoro-wa-Ma, nakĩo kĩrĩma kĩa Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe gĩgeetagwo Kĩrĩma Gĩtheru.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 65:20">Isa 65:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: “Athuuri na atumia arĩa akũrũ mũno nĩmagaikara njĩra-inĩ cia Jerusalemu rĩngĩ, o mũndũ anyiitĩte mũtirima wake na guoko nĩ ũndũ wa gũkũra mũno. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 30:20">Jer 30:20</ref>; <ref loc="JER 31:13">31:13</ref></char></note>Njĩra cia itũũra rĩu inene ikaiyũra tũhĩĩ na tũirĩtu tũgĩthaaka.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 118:23">Thab 118:23</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 126:1-3">126:1-3</ref></char>
    </note>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: “Hĩndĩ ĩyo ũndũ ũcio no woneke ũrĩ wa magegania nĩ matigari ma andũ acio, no Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekũũria atĩrĩ, harĩ niĩ-rĩ, ũndũ ũcio no woneke ũrĩ wa magegania?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 11:11">Isa 11:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: “Nĩngahonokia andũ akwa kuuma mabũrũri ma mwena wa irathĩro na wa ithũĩro. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 2:11">Zek 2:11</ref>; <ref loc="JER 11:4">Jer 11:4</ref></char></note>Nĩngamacookia matũũre Jerusalemu; nao magaatuĩka andũ akwa na niĩ nduĩke Ngai wao wa kwĩhokeka na mũthingu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: “Inyuĩ arĩa mũraigua ciugo ici ciaririo nĩ anabii arĩa maarĩ kuo rĩrĩa mũthingi wa nyũmba ya Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe wahaandirwo-rĩ, gĩai na hinya nĩgeetha hekarũ yakwo. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 5:10">Isa 5:10</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 15:5">2Maũ 15:5</ref></char></note>Mbere ya hĩndĩ ĩyo gũtiarĩ irĩhi rĩa mũndũ kana rĩa nyamũ. Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩarutire wĩra wake na thayũ nĩ ũndũ wa thũ ciake, tondũ nĩndatũmĩte o mũndũ o mũndũ okĩrĩre ũrĩa ũngĩ. <verse number="11" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, rĩu ndigũcooka kũherithia matigari ma andũ aya ta ũrĩa ndeekaga tene.” Ũguo nĩguo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOL 2:22">Joel 2:22</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 27:28">Kĩam 27:28</ref></char>
    </note>“Mbeũ nĩĩgakũra wega, naguo mũthabibũ nĩũgaciara matunda maguo, na tĩĩri nĩũkaruta magetha maguo, narĩo igũrũ nĩrĩgatatia ime. Ngaaheana maũndũ maya mothe matuĩke igai rĩa matigari ma andũ aya. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 5:27">Ndar 5:27</ref>; <ref loc="JER 42:18">Jer 42:18</ref></char></note>O ta ũrĩa mũkoretwo mũkĩonwo ta mũrĩ arume mũrĩ gatagatĩ-inĩ ka ndũrĩrĩ, wee Juda na Isiraeli-rĩ, noguo ngaamũhonokia, na nĩmũgatuĩka kĩrathimo. Mũtigetigĩre, no gĩai na hinya.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: “O ta ũrĩa ndaatuĩte atĩ nĩngũmũrehere mwanangĩko, na ndiigana kũigua tha rĩrĩa maithe manyu mandakaririe-rĩ,” Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga atĩrĩ, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 29:11">Jer 29:11</ref></char></note>“nĩ ũndũ ũcio rĩu nĩnduĩte nĩngwĩka Jerusalemu na Juda maũndũ mega rĩngĩ. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio tigai gwĩtigĩra. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:25">Aef 4:25</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 7:9">Zek 7:9</ref></char></note>Maya nĩmo maũndũ marĩa mũgwĩka: aranagĩriai ũhoro wa ma mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ, na mũtuage ciira wa ma na wa kĩhooto maciirĩro-inĩ manyu; <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 3:29">Thim 3:29</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 5:4">Zek 5:4</ref></char></note>mũtikanaciirĩre gwĩka mũndũ wa itũũra rĩanyu ũũru, na mũtikanende kwĩhĩta na maheeni. Niĩ nĩthũire maũndũ macio mothe,” ũguo nĩguo Jehova ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩyanginyĩrire rĩngĩ, ngĩĩrwo atĩrĩ: <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2KI 25:7">2Ath 25:7</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 30:11">Thab 30:11</ref></char></note>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: “Mahinda ma kwĩhinga kũrĩa irio mweri wa kana, na wa gatano, na wa mũgwanja na wa ikũmi-rĩ, magaatuĩka mahinda ma gũcanjamũka na kũrũũhia, na ma maruga ma gĩkeno harĩ Juda. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio endagai ũhoro wa ma na wa thayũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: “Andũ aingĩ na atũũri a matũũra maingĩ manene nĩ magooka, <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 7:2">Zek 7:2</ref>; <ref loc="JER 26:19">Jer 26:19</ref></char></note>nao atũũri a itũũra rĩmwe inene magaathiĩ itũũra rĩngĩ inene moige atĩrĩ, ‘Rekei tũthiĩ o rĩu tũgathaithe Jehova na tũkarongoorie Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe. Niĩ mwene nĩngũthiĩ.’ <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 86:9">Thab 86:9</ref></char></note>Irĩndĩ na ndũrĩrĩ irĩ hinya nĩ igooka Jerusalemu kũrongooria Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe na kũmũthaitha.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 102:22">Thab 102:22</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 14:25">1Akor 14:25</ref></char>
    </note>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga ũũ: “Matukũ-inĩ macio andũ ikũmi kuuma thiomi-inĩ ciothe na ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ ciothe nĩmakanyiita Mũyahudi ũmwe, marũmie gĩcũrĩ gĩa kanjũ yake na mamwĩre atĩrĩ, ‘Reke tũthiĩ nawe, tondũ nĩtũiguĩte atĩ Ngai arĩ hamwe na inyuĩ.’ ”</para>
  <chapter number="9" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gũtuĩrwo gwa Thũ cia Isiraeli</para>
  <para style="s2">Ũrathi</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 17:1">Isa 17:1</ref>; <ref loc="AMO 1:5">Amos 1:5</ref></char>
    </note>Ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova nĩyũkĩrĩire bũrũri wa Hadaraka,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ĩgakinyĩrĩra Dameski:</para>
  <para style="q1">nĩgũkorwo maitho ma andũ, na ma mĩhĩrĩga yothe ya Isiraeli macũthĩrĩirie Jehova,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 49:23">Jer 49:23</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 28:1-19">Ezek 28:1-19</ref></char>
    </note>na ĩgakinyĩrĩra Hamathu o nakuo, itũũra rĩrĩa rĩhakanĩte nakuo,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ĩgakinyĩrĩra Turo na Sidoni, o na gũtuĩka andũ akuo maarĩ oogĩ mũno.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 27:16">Ayub 27:16</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 28:4">Ezek 28:4</ref></char>
    </note>Andũ a Turo nĩmeyakĩire kĩĩgitĩro kĩrũmu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na makeigĩra hĩba cia betha nyingĩ ta rũkũngũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na thahabu nyingĩ ta mahuti ma njĩra-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 23:1">Isa 23:1</ref>; <ref loc="JER 25:22">Jer 25:22</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩakarĩtunya ũtonga warĩo,</para>
  <para style="q2">na aanange ũhoti warĩo wa iria-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">narĩo itũũra rĩu nĩrĩgacinwo na mwaki.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Ashikeloni nĩrĩkeyonera ũhoro ũcio na rĩĩtigĩre,</para>
  <para style="q2">Gaza nĩrĩkehũũrithania nĩ ruo rũnene,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na Ekironi o narĩo, nĩgũkorwo mwĩhoko warĩo nĩũkahooha.</para>
  <para style="q1">Gaza nĩrĩkoorwo nĩ mũthamaki warĩo,</para>
  <para style="q2">narĩo Ashikeloni nĩrĩgathaamwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 14:30">Isa 14:30</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Andũ a bũrũri ũngĩ nĩmagatũũra Ashidodi,</para>
  <para style="q2">na niĩ nĩnganiina mwĩtĩĩo wa Afilisti.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 25:2">Ayub 25:2</ref>; <ref loc="ZEP 2:4">Zef 2:4</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩngaruta thakame tũnua-inĩ twao,</para>
  <para style="q2">na irio iria ngaananie ndĩcirute gatagatĩ ka magego mao.</para>
  <para style="q1">Andũ arĩa magaatigara magaatuĩka a Ngai witũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na matuĩke atongoria a Juda,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao andũ a Ekironi makahaana ta andũ a Jebusi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 26:1">Isa 26:1</ref>; <ref loc="JOL 3:17">Joel 3:17</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, nĩngagitĩra nyũmba yakwa</para>
  <para style="q2">kuuma kũrĩ mbũtũ iria imarehagĩra mbaara.</para>
  <para style="q1">Gũtirĩ hĩndĩ ĩngĩ mũhinyanĩrĩria agaacooka gũtooria andũ akwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo rĩu nĩndĩĩoneire ũrĩa maanahinyĩrĩrio.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũũka kwa Mũthamaki wa Zayuni</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 9:6-7">Isa 9:6-7</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 21:5">Math 21:5</ref></char>
    </note>Kena mũno, wee Mwarĩ wa Zayuni!</para>
  <para style="q2">Anĩrĩra, wee Mwarĩ wa Jerusalemu!</para>
  <para style="q1">Atĩrĩrĩ, mũthamaki waku nĩarooka kũrĩ we,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ mũthingu na arĩ na ũhonokio,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ mũhooreri na akuuĩtwo nĩ ndigiri,</para>
  <para style="q2">agaikarĩra njaũ ya ndigiri.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HOS 1:7">Hos 1:7</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 2:4">Isa 2:4</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩngeheria ngaari cia ita kuuma Efiraimu,</para>
  <para style="q2">na njeherie mbarathi cia mbaara kuuma Jerusalemu,</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ũta wa mbaara-rĩ, nĩũkoinangwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nake aanĩrĩre thayũ ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q2">Wathani wake-rĩ, ũgaatambũrũka kuuma iria rĩmwe nginya rĩrĩa rĩngĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na kuuma Rũũĩ rwa Farati o nginya ituri cia thĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 24:8">Thaam 24:8</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 22:20">Luk 22:20</ref></char>
    </note>No ha ũhoro waku-rĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa thakame ya kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa ndarĩkanĩire nawe,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩngoohorithia andũ aku arĩa mohetwo, moime irima rĩu rĩtarĩ maaĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Cookai kĩĩhitho-inĩ kĩanyu kĩrĩa kĩrũmu, inyuĩ muohetwo mũrĩ na mwĩhoko;</para>
  <para style="q2">o na rĩu nguuga atĩrĩ, nĩngamũcookeria indo cianyu maita meerĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOL 3:6">Joel 3:6</ref>; <ref loc="JER 51:20">Jer 51:20</ref></char>
    </note>Ngaagonya Juda o taarĩ ũta wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">nake Efiraimu atuĩke ta mĩguĩ ya ũta ũcio, ndĩmaiyũrie kuo.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩngarahũra ariũ aku, wee Zayuni,</para>
  <para style="q2">mokĩrĩre ariũ aku wee Mũyunani,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ngũtue ta rũhiũ rwa njora rwa njamba ĩrĩ hinya.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jehova Nĩakoimĩra</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jehova nĩakoonwo arĩ igũrũ rĩao;</para>
  <para style="q2">mũguĩ wake ũkaarathũka ta rũheni.</para>
  <para style="q1">Mwathani Jehova nĩakahuha karumbeta;</para>
  <para style="q2">agaathiĩ arĩ ihuhũkanio-inĩ cia mwena wa gũthini,</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 37:35">Isa 37:35</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 27:2">Thaam 27:2</ref></char>
    </note>nake Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩakamagitĩra.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nao makaamaniina biũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na matooranie na kũmahũũra na mahiga ma kĩgũtha.</para>
  <para style="q1">Makaanyua na manegene ta marĩĩtwo nĩ ndibei;</para>
  <para style="q2">makaiyũrĩrĩrio ta mbakũri</para>
  <para style="q2">ĩrĩa ĩhũthagĩrwo kũminjaminjĩria koine cia kĩgongona.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 31:11">Jer 31:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jehova Ngai wao nĩakamahonokia mũthenya ũcio,</para>
  <para style="q2">marĩ andũ a rũũru rwake.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩmagakengaga bũrũri-inĩ wake,</para>
  <para style="q2">ta mahiga ma goro marĩ thũmbĩ-inĩ ya mũthamaki.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Kaĩ nĩmagakorwo marĩ a kwendeka, na mathakarĩte-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="q2">Irio cia mĩgũnda nĩigatũma aanake magaacĩre,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo ndibei ya mũhihano ĩtũme airĩtu o nao magaacĩre.</para>
  <chapter number="10" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jehova Nĩakamenyerera Juda</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 26:4">Alaw 26:4</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 14:9">Ayub 14:9</ref></char>
    </note>Hooyai Jehova oirie mbura hĩndĩ ya kĩmera kĩa mbere;</para>
  <para style="q2">Jehova nĩwe ũtũmaga kũgĩe matu ma mbura ya kĩhuhũkanio.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩoiragĩria andũ mbura,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akahe mũndũ o wothe irio cia mũgũnda.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 21:21">Ezek 21:21</ref>; <ref loc="HOS 3:4">Hos 3:4</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 9:36">Math 9:36</ref></char>
    </note>Mĩhianano ya kũhooywo yaragia maheeni,</para>
  <para style="q2">ago moonaga cioneki itarĩ cia ma,</para>
  <para style="q1">maaragia ũhoro wa irooto itarĩ cia ma;</para>
  <para style="q2">kũhoorerania kwao no gwa tũhũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩ ũndũ ũcio andũ maturuuraga ta ngʼondu,</para>
  <para style="q2">makahinyĩrĩrĩka nĩ ũndũ wa kwaga mũrĩithi.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 25:34">Jer 25:34</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Marakara makwa nĩmakanĩte nĩ ũndũ wa arĩithi,</para>
  <para style="q2">na niĩ nĩngaherithia atongoria acio;</para>
  <para style="q1">nĩgũkorwo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe nĩakamenyerera</para>
  <para style="q2">rũũru rwake, nĩruo andũ a nyũmba ya Juda,</para>
  <para style="q2">na atũme matuĩke ta mbarathi ĩgwĩtĩĩa ĩrĩ mbaara-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 118:22">Thab 118:22</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 22:23">Isa 22:23</ref></char>
    </note>Thĩinĩ wa Juda nĩgũkoima ũrĩa ũgaatuĩka ihiga rĩa koine,</para>
  <para style="q2">na kuuma kũrĩ we kuume higĩ cia kwamba hema,</para>
  <para style="q2">ningĩ kuume ũta wa mbaara,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kuume mũndũ o wothe wa gwathana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2SA 22:43">2Sam 22:43</ref>; <ref loc="HAG 2:22">Hag 2:22</ref></char>
    </note>Marĩ hamwe magaatuĩka ta njamba cia ita irĩ hinya,</para>
  <para style="q2">marangĩrĩrie thũ ciao ndoro-inĩ ya njĩra hĩndĩ ya mbaara.</para>
  <para style="q1">Tondũ Jehova agaakorwo hamwe nao,</para>
  <para style="q2">makaarũa na mangʼaũranie ahaici a mbarathi.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 102:13">Thab 102:13</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 13:9">Zek 13:9</ref></char>
    </note>“Nĩngekĩra nyũmba ya Juda hinya,</para>
  <para style="q2">na honokie nyũmba ya Jusufu.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩngamacookia kwao,</para>
  <para style="q2">tondũ nĩndĩmaiguĩrĩire tha.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nao magaikara ta itarĩ ndaamarega,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo niĩ nĩ niĩ Jehova Ngai wao,</para>
  <para style="q2">na nĩngamacookeria mahooya mao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Andũ a Efiraimu magaatuĩka ta njamba cia ita,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio ngoro ciao icanjamũke ta andũ manyuĩte ndibei.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ciana ciao nĩikoona ũndũ ũcio ikene;</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio ngoro ciao nĩigakenera Jehova.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 5:26">Isa 5:26</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 36:11">Ezek 36:11</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩngameta ndĩmacookanĩrĩrie.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ti-itherũ nĩngamakũũra;</para>
  <para style="q1">nao nĩmakaingĩha o ta ũrĩa maarĩ mbere.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 44:21">Isa 44:21</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 6:9">Ezek 6:9</ref></char>
    </note>O na ingĩkamaharaganĩria ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">marĩ o kũu mabũrũri ma kũraya no makaandirikana.</para>
  <para style="q1">O, hamwe na ciana ciao nĩmakahonoka</para>
  <para style="q2">na macooke kwao.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 11:11">Isa 11:11</ref>; <ref loc="JER 50:19">Jer 50:19</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩngamacookia kuuma Misiri,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndĩmacookanĩrĩrie kuuma Ashuri.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩngamarehe bũrũri wa Gileadi na wa Lebanoni,</para>
  <para style="q2">o nginya mage ũikaro ũngĩmaigana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 19:5-7">Isa 19:5-7</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 30:13">Ezek 30:13</ref></char>
    </note>Magaatuĩkanĩria iria rĩa thĩĩna;</para>
  <para style="q2">makũmbĩ ma iria nĩmakahoorerio,</para>
  <para style="q2">nakuo kũrĩa Rũũĩ rwa Nili rũrikĩte nĩgũkahũa.</para>
  <para style="q1">Mwĩtĩĩo wa Ashuri nĩũkaharũrũkio,</para>
  <para style="q2">nayo thimbũ ya ũthamaki wa Misiri nĩĩkeherio.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 30:24">Ezek 30:24</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 4:5">Mik 4:5</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩngamekĩra hinya ndĩmomĩrĩrie thĩinĩ wa Jehova,</para>
  <para style="q2">na thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩake nĩmagetwara,”</para>
  <para style="q4">ũguo nĩguo Jehova ekuuga.</para>
  <chapter number="11" style="c"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 31:3">Ezek 31:3</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 36:19">2Maũ 36:19</ref></char>
    </note>Wee, Lebanoni-rĩ, hingũra mĩrango yaku,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgeetha mwaki ũcine mĩtarakwa yaku, ũmĩniine!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 2:13">Isa 2:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩra, wee mũthithinda, nĩgũkorwo mũtarakwa nĩũgwĩte;</para>
  <para style="q2">mĩtĩ ĩrĩa mĩrũngarũ nĩmĩanange!</para>
  <para style="q1">Rĩrai inyuĩ mĩgandi ya Bashani;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo mĩtĩ ya mũtitũ ũrĩa mũtumanu nĩĩtemetwo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 2:15">Jer 2:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ta thikĩrĩriai ũrĩa arĩithi maraarĩra, makĩgirĩkaga:</para>
  <para style="q2">ũrĩithio wao ũrĩa mũnoru nĩwanangĩtwo!</para>
  <para style="q1">Ta thikĩrĩriai mũraramo wa mĩrũũthi;</para>
  <para style="q2">gĩthaka kĩrĩa kĩruru kĩa Jorodani nĩkĩanange!</para>
  <para style="s1">Arĩithi Eerĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Jehova Ngai wakwa ekuuga ũũ: “Rĩithia rũũru rũrĩa rũtuĩrĩirwo gũthĩnjwo. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 50:7">Jer 50:7</ref></char></note>Arĩa macigũraga nĩo macithĩnjaga na matione wa kũmaherithia. Arĩa maciendagia moigaga atĩrĩ, ‘Jehova arogoocwo, niĩ ndĩ mũtongu!’ Arĩithi ene cio maticiiguagĩra tha. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 9:19-21">Isa 9:19-21</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 5:8">Mik 5:8</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ndikaiguĩra andũ a bũrũri ũcio tha rĩngĩ,” ũguo nĩguo Jehova ekuuga. “Nĩnganeana mũndũ o kũrĩ mũndũ wa itũũra rĩake na kũrĩ mũthamaki wake. Nĩmakahinyĩrĩria bũrũri ũcio, na ndikamahonokia kuuma moko-inĩ mao.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngĩrĩithia rũũru rũu rwatuĩrĩirwo gũthĩnjwo, na makĩria iria ciahinyĩrĩirio cia rũũru rũu. Ngĩcooka ngĩoya thanju igĩrĩ, rũmwe ngĩrwĩta Ũtugi na rũrĩa rũngĩ ngĩrwĩta Ũiguano, na niĩ ngĩrĩithia rũũru rũu. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 14:5">Ezek 14:5</ref></char></note>Ihinda rĩa mweri ũmwe nĩndeheririe arĩithi acio atatũ.</para>
  <para style="p">Naruo rũũru rũgĩĩthũũra mũno, na niĩ ngĩnogio nĩo, <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 9:20">Isa 9:20</ref>; <ref loc="JER 43:11">Jer 43:11</ref></char></note>ngiuga atĩrĩ, “Ndigũcooka gũtuĩka mũrĩithi wanyu. Iria cia gũkua nĩikue, na iria cia gũthira nĩithire. Iria igũtigara-rĩ, nĩirĩane cio nyene.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 89:39">Thab 89:39</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ ngĩoya rũthanju rwakwa rũrĩa rwetagwo Ũtugi, ngĩruunania icunjĩ igĩrĩ, ngĩtharia kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa ndarĩkanĩire na ndũrĩrĩ ciothe. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Gĩatharirio o ro mũthenya ũcio, na nĩ ũndũ ũcio arĩa maahinyĩrĩirio a rũũru rũu, arĩa maanjũũthĩrĩirie, makĩmenya atĩ ĩyo yarĩ ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:15">Math 26:15</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 23:16">Kĩam 23:16</ref></char>
    </note>Ngĩcooka ngĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Mũngĩona nĩ kwagĩrĩire, Heei mũcaara wakwa, na aakorwo ti ũguo-rĩ, ikarai naguo.” Nĩ ũndũ ũcio makĩndĩha mũcaara wa icunjĩ mĩrongo ĩtatũ cia betha.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:9-10">Math 27:9-10</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 21:32">Thaam 21:32</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jehova akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Ikĩria mũũmbi wa nyũngũ mbeeca icio”: ĩ thogora ũcio mwega moonire nĩũnjiganĩte! Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngĩoya icunjĩ icio mĩrongo ĩtatũ cia betha, ngĩciikĩria mũũmbi kũu nyũmba-inĩ ya Jehova.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Ningĩ ngiunania rũthanju rwakwa rwa keerĩ rũrĩa rwetagwo Ũiguano, ngĩthũkia ũrũmwe gatagatĩ ka Juda na Isiraeli.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Ningĩ Jehova akĩnjĩĩra atĩrĩ, “Oya o rĩngĩ indo cia mũrĩithi mũkĩĩgu. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo nĩngwarahũra mũrĩithi bũrũri-inĩ ũyũ, ũrĩa ũtakarũmbũiya ngʼondu iria ciũrĩte, kana acarie tũgondu, kana ohe iria ndiihie, o na kana arĩithie iria ngʼima, we no kũrĩa arĩrĩĩaga nyama cia ngʼondu iria noru, agĩcikũũraga mahũngũ.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 23:1">Jer 23:1</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 13:1">Isa 13:1</ref></char>
    </note>“Kaĩ mũrĩithi ũcio wa tũhũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũrĩa ũtiganagĩria rũũru, arĩ na haaro-ĩ!</para>
  <para style="q1">Guoko gwake na riitho rĩake rĩa ũrĩo irotemwo na rũhiũ rwa njora!</para>
  <para style="q2">Guoko gwake nĩgũkonja biũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">na riitho rĩake rĩa ũrĩo rĩtuĩke itumumu biũ.”</para>
  <chapter number="12" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Thũ cia Jerusalemu Kũniinwo</para>
  <para style="s2">Ũrathi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 104:2">Thab 104:2</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 57:16">Isa 57:16</ref></char>
    </note>Ĩno nĩyo ndũmĩrĩri ya Jehova ĩkoniĩ Isiraeli. Jehova, ũrĩa watambũrũkirie igũrũ, na akĩhaanda gĩtina gĩa thĩ ĩno, o na akĩũmba roho thĩinĩ wa mũndũ, ekuuga ũũ: <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 60:3">Thab 60:3</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 51:23">Isa 51:23</ref></char></note>“Nĩngũtua Jerusalemu ta gĩkombe kĩa ndibei gĩa gũtũma arĩa othe magũthiũrũrũkĩirie matũgũũge. Juda o ũndũ ũmwe na Jerusalemu nĩgũkarigiicĩrio nĩ thũ. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 14:2">Zek 14:2</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 29:8">Isa 29:8</ref></char></note>Mũthenya ũcio, rĩrĩa ndũrĩrĩ ciothe cia thĩ igaacookanĩrĩra irĩũkĩrĩre, nĩngatua Jerusalemu ihiga rĩtangĩenyenyeka kũrĩ ndũrĩrĩ ciothe. Arĩa othe makaageria kũrĩenyenyia nĩmakeguraria mũno. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 76:6">Thab 76:6</ref></char></note>Mũthenya ũcio-rĩ, nĩngamakia mbarathi o yothe ĩhahũke, nake mũmĩhaici ndũme agũrũke,” ũguo nĩguo Jehova ekuuga. “Nĩngarangĩra nyũmba ya Juda, no mbarathi ciothe cia ndũrĩrĩ ndĩcitue ndumumu. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 30:24">Ezek 30:24</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo atongoria a Juda makeĩĩra na ngoro atĩrĩ, ‘Andũ a Jerusalemu nĩmagĩte na hinya nĩ ũndũ wa Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe, o we Ngai wao.’</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="OBA 1:18">Obad 1:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Mũthenya ũcio nĩngatũma atongoria a Juda mahaane ta nyũngũ ĩiyũrĩte mwaki ĩrĩ riiko, na ndũme mahaane ta gĩcinga gĩgwakana kĩrĩ thĩinĩ wa itĩĩa cia ngano. Makaaniina andũ arĩa othe marĩthiũrũrũkĩirie mwena wa ũrĩo na mwena wa ũmotho, no rĩrĩ, andũ a Jerusalemu matigaakorwo na ũgwati o na hanini marĩ kũu Jerusalemu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>“Jehova akaamba kũhonokia andũ arĩa matũũraga Juda, nĩgeetha gĩtĩĩo kĩa nyũmba ya Daudi na kĩa aikari a Jerusalemu gĩtikananenehe gũkĩra kĩa andũ a Juda. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 9:15">Zek 9:15</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 7:8">Mik 7:8</ref></char></note>Mũthenya ũcio Jehova nĩakagitĩra andũ arĩa matũũraga Jerusalemu, nĩgeetha arĩa maagĩte hinya mũno gatagatĩ-inĩ kao makahaana ta Daudi, nayo nyũmba ya Daudi ĩkahaana o ta Ngai, ĩhaane ta mũraika wa Jehova amatongoretie. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Mũthenya ũcio nĩngoimagara nganiine ndũrĩrĩ ciothe iria igookĩrĩra itũũra rĩa Jerusalemu.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũrĩrĩra ũrĩa Maathecire</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOL 2:28-29">Joel 2:28-29</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 19:34">Joh 19:34</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 19:37">37</ref></char>
    </note>“Na nĩngaitĩrĩria nyũmba ya Daudi na arĩa othe matũũraga itũũra rĩa Jerusalemu roho wa gũtugana na wagũthaithana. Nao nĩmakerorera ũrĩa maathecire, na nĩmakamũrĩrĩra marĩ na ruo o ta ũrĩa mũndũ arĩragĩra mwana wa mũmwe, na magĩe na kĩeha kĩnene o ta ũrĩa mũndũ ethikagĩra akuĩrĩirwo nĩ mwana wake wa irigithathi. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2KI 23:29">2Ath 23:29</ref></char></note>Mũthenya ũcio nĩgũgakorwo kĩrĩro kĩnene kũu Jerusalemu, o ta kĩrĩro kĩrĩa kĩarĩ Hadadi-Rimoni<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Hadadi-Rimoni nĩkuo andũ maacakaĩire gĩkuũ kĩa Josia (2Maũ 35:22, 24, 25).</char></note> o kũu werũ-inĩ wa Megido. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Bũrũri ũcio nĩũkagĩa na kĩrĩro, o mbarĩ o mbarĩ ĩrĩre ĩrĩ iiki, na atumia ao marĩ oiki: mbarĩ ya nyũmba ya Daudi ĩrĩre ĩrĩ iiki na atumia ao marĩ oiki, mbarĩ ya nyũmba ya Nathani ĩrĩre ĩrĩ iiki, na atumia ao marĩ oiki, <verse number="13" style="v"/>na mbarĩ ya nyũmba ya Lawi ĩrĩre ĩrĩ iiki, na atumia ao marĩ oiki, mbarĩ ya Shimei ĩrĩre ĩrĩ iiki, na atumia ao marĩ oiki, <verse number="14" style="v"/>na mbarĩ icio ingĩ ciothe itigaire o mbarĩ o mbarĩ ĩrĩre ĩrĩ iiki, na atumia ao marĩ oiki.</para>
  <chapter number="13" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gũtherio kwa Mehia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 51:2">Thab 51:2</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 9:14">Ahib 9:14</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũthenya ũcio gĩthima nĩgĩgathikũrio nĩ ũndũ wa nyũmba ya Daudi o na nĩ ũndũ wa andũ arĩa matũũraga Jerusalemu, gĩthima gĩa kũmatheria mehia o na thaahu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 43:12">Jer 43:12</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 22:22">1Ath 22:22</ref></char>
    </note>Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga atĩrĩ, “Mũthenya ũcio nĩnganiina marĩĩtwa ma mĩhianano ya kũhooywo mathire bũrũri-inĩ, na matigacooka kũririkanwo rĩngĩ. Nĩngeheria anabii hamwe na roho ũcio wa thaahu, mathire bũrũri-inĩ. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 23:34">Jer 23:34</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, kũngĩgaakorwo na mũndũ ũrathiĩ na mbere na kũratha mohoro-rĩ, ithe na nyina, arĩa mamũciarĩte, nĩ makaamwĩra atĩrĩ, ‘No nginya ũkue, nĩ ũndũ nĩwarĩtie maheeni ũkĩgwetaga rĩĩtwa rĩa Jehova.’ Rĩrĩa akaaratha mohoro-rĩ, aciari ake mwene nĩmakamũtheeca na rũhiũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 3:4">Math 3:4</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 12:24">Ezek 12:24</ref></char>
    </note>“Mũthenya ũcio mũnabii o wothe nĩagaconoka nĩ ũndũ wa kĩoneki kĩa ũrathi wake. Ndakehumba nguo ya maguoya ya mũnabii nĩguo aheenie andũ. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="AMO 7:14">Amos 7:14</ref></char></note>Akoigaga atĩrĩ, ‘Niĩ ndirĩ mũnabii, ndĩ mũrĩmi, ndũũragio nĩ mũgũnda kuuma ũnini-inĩ wakwa.’ <verse number="6" style="v"/>Nake mũndũ angĩkamũũria atĩrĩ, ‘Ironda ici irĩ mwĩrĩ waku nĩ cia kĩ?’ we agaacookia atĩrĩ, ‘Ironda ici ndagĩĩrĩire nyũmba-inĩ ya arata akwa.’</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũrĩithi Kũringwo, na Ngʼondu Kũhurunjũka</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 34:5">Isa 34:5</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:31">Math 26:31</ref></char>
    </note>“Arahũka, wee rũhiũ rwa njora, ũũkĩrĩre mũrĩithi wakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">ũkĩrĩra mũndũ ũcio wa hakuhĩ na niĩ!”</para>
  <para style="q2">ũguo nĩguo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ringa mũrĩithi, nacio ngʼondu nĩikũhurunjũka,</para>
  <para style="q2">nakuo guoko gwakwa ndĩkwerekerie kũrĩ tũgondu, ndĩtũũkĩrĩre.”</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 5:2-4">Ezek 5:2-4</ref>, <ref loc="EZK 5:12">12</ref></char>
    </note>Jehova ekuuga atĩrĩ, “Bũrũri-inĩ guothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ icunjĩ igĩrĩ thĩinĩ wa ithatũ nĩmakooragwo, mathire;</para>
  <para style="q2">no rĩrĩ, gĩcunjĩ kĩmwe gĩa ithatũ nĩgĩgatigara kuo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 1:6-7">1Pet 1:6-7</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 50:15">Thab 50:15</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 26:12">Alaw 26:12</ref></char>
    </note>Gĩcunjĩ kĩu gĩa ithatũ kĩa andũ nĩngakĩhĩtũkĩria mwaki-inĩ;</para>
  <para style="q2">ngaamatheria ta betha, na ndĩmagerie ta ũrĩa thahabu igeragio.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩmagakaĩra rĩĩtwa rĩakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">na niĩ nĩngametĩka;</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩngoiga atĩrĩ, ‘Aya nĩ andũ akwa,’</para>
  <para style="q2">nao moige atĩrĩ, ‘Jehova nĩwe Ngai witũ.’ ”</para>
  <chapter number="14" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jehova Nĩegũũka Athamake</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 13:6">Isa 13:6</ref>; <ref loc="MAL 4:1">Mal 4:1</ref></char>
    </note>Atĩrĩrĩ, mũthenya wa Jehova nĩũrooka, rĩrĩa indo cianyu igaatahwo na igayanĩrwo gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 2:3">Isa 2:3</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 34:29">Kĩam 34:29</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩngongania ndũrĩrĩ ciothe ciũkĩrĩre itũũra rĩa Jerusalemu, ihũũrane narĩo; itũũra rĩu inene nĩrĩkanyiitwo nĩ thũ, na indo cia nyũmba ciũngũrũrio nao andũ-a-nja manyiitwo na hinya. Andũ nuthu ya itũũra nĩmagathaamio, no andũ acio angĩ matikeherio itũũra-inĩ rĩu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Jehova nĩakoimagara, okĩrĩre ndũrĩrĩ icio arũe nacio, o ta ũrĩa arũaga mũthenya wa mbaara. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 11:23">Ezek 11:23</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 16:31">Ndar 16:31</ref></char></note>Mũthenya ũcio-rĩ, Jehova nĩakarũgama Kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩa Mĩtamaiyũ, mwena wa irathĩro wa Jerusalemu. Nakĩo Kĩrĩma kĩu kĩa Mĩtamaiyũ nĩgĩgatũkana maita meerĩ kuuma mwena wa irathĩro nginya mwena wa ithũĩro; naho hagĩe mũkuru mũnene, nuthu ĩmwe ya kĩrĩma ĩthiĩ mwena wa gathigathini, nayo nuthu ĩyo ĩngĩ ĩthiĩ mwena wa gũthini. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="AMO 1:1">Amos 1:1</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 16:27">Math 16:27</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 25:31">25:31</ref></char></note>Mũkoorĩra mũkuru-inĩ ũcio wa kĩrĩma gĩakwa tondũ ũgaakinya o Azeli. Mũkoora o ta ũrĩa mworĩire gĩthingithia matukũ-inĩ ma Uzia, mũthamaki wa Juda. Nake Jehova Ngai wakwa nĩagooka, arĩ hamwe na andũ arĩa atheru othe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Mũthenya ũcio gũtigakorwo na ũtheri kana heho o na kana mbaa. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 30:7">Jer 30:7</ref>; <ref loc="REV 21:23-25">Kũg 21:23-25</ref>; <ref loc="REV 22:5">22:5</ref></char></note>Ũcio ũgaakorwo ũrĩ mũthenya wa mwanya, ũtarĩ mũthenya kana ũtukũ, mũthenya ũũĩo nĩ Jehova. Hwaĩ-inĩ wakinya, nĩgũkagĩa na ũtheri.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 47:1-2">Ezek 47:1-2</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:38">Joh 7:38</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 8:22">Kĩam 8:22</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthenya ũcio maaĩ ma muoyo nĩmagatherera moimĩte Jerusalemu; nuthu yamo yerekere iria-inĩ rĩa mwena wa irathĩro, nayo nuthu ĩyo ĩngĩ yerekere iria-inĩ rĩa mwena wa ithũĩro. Maaĩ macio magathereraga hĩndĩ ya ũrugarĩ na hĩndĩ ya heho.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="REV 11:15">Kũg 11:15</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:5-6">Aef 4:5-6</ref></char>
    </note>Jehova nĩwe ũgaatuĩka mũthamaki wa thĩ yothe. Mũthenya ũcio gũgaakorwo Jehova arĩ o we wiki, narĩo rĩĩtwa rĩake rĩkorwo no rĩo riiki.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 15:22">1Ath 15:22</ref>; <ref loc="JER 20:2">Jer 20:2</ref></char>
    </note>Bũrũri wothe kuuma Geba nginya Rimoni, mwena wa gũthini wa Jerusalemu, ũkaahaana ta Araba. No rĩrĩ, itũũra rĩa Jerusalemu nĩrĩgatũũgĩrio na rĩtũũre o hau rĩrĩ, kuuma Kĩhingo-inĩ kĩa Benjamini nginya harĩa Kĩhingo kĩa Mbere kĩrĩ, o nginya Kĩhingo-inĩ gĩa Koine, na kuuma mũthiringo ũrĩa mũraaya na igũrũ wa Hananeli gũthiĩ nginya ihihĩro-inĩ cia ndibei cia mũthamaki. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Itũũra rĩu rĩgaatuĩka rĩa gũtũũrwo; rĩtikaanangwo hĩndĩ ĩngĩ. Itũũra rĩa Jerusalemu rĩgaatũũra rĩtarĩ na ũgwati.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 28:22">Gũcook 28:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, ũyũ nĩguo mũthiro ũrĩa Jehova akaahũũra ndũrĩrĩ ciothe naguo, iria cianarũa na Jerusalemu: Mĩĩrĩ yao ĩkaabuthaga o marũgamĩte na magũrũ mao, maitho mao namo mabuthĩre marima-inĩ mamo, nacio nĩmĩ ciao ikaabutha irĩ tũnua-inĩ twao. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 35:5">Kĩam 35:5</ref>; <ref loc="JDG 7:22">Atiir 7:22</ref></char></note>Mũthenya ũcio-rĩ, Jehova nĩakahũũra andũ na kĩmako kĩnene. O mũndũ nĩakaguthũkĩra guoko kwa mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ akũnyiite, nao matharĩkanĩre marũe. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 12:2">Zek 12:2</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 23:18">Isa 23:18</ref></char></note>Andũ a Juda o nao nĩmakarũĩra kũu Jerusalemu. Ũtonga wa ndũrĩrĩ iria irigiicĩirie kũu nĩũkonganio, naguo nĩ ũtonga mũingĩ wa thahabu, na wa betha na wa nguo. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ZEC 14:12">Zek 14:12</ref></char></note>Mũthiro o ta ũcio nĩũkaniina mbarathi na nyũmbũ, na ngamĩĩra na ndigiri, na nyamũ ciothe iria igaakorwo kambĩ-inĩ icio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2KI 19:31">2Ath 19:31</ref>; <ref loc="OBA 1:21">Obad 1:21</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 4:2">Mik 4:2</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ-rĩ, matigari ma ndũrĩrĩ icio ciothe iria cianatharĩkĩra Jerusalemu makaambataga mwaka o mwaka kũhooya Mũthamaki, o we Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe, na gũkũngũĩra Gĩathĩ gĩa Ithũnũ. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="AMO 4:7">Amos 4:7</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 32:23">2Maũ 32:23</ref></char></note>Kũngĩkaagĩa andũ gũkũ thĩ matakaambata Jerusalemu kũhooya Mũthamaki, o we Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe-rĩ, kwao gũtikoira mbura. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 27:29">Kĩam 27:29</ref></char></note>Andũ a Misiri mangĩkaaga gũthiĩ kũnyiitanĩra na arĩa angĩ-rĩ, kwao gũtikoira mbura. Jehova nĩakamarehera mũthiro ũrĩa ahũũraga ndũrĩrĩ naguo iria itaambataga gũkũngũĩra Gĩathĩ kĩu gĩa Ithũnũ. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Rĩĩrĩ nĩrĩo rĩgaakorwo rĩrĩ iherithia rĩa bũrũri wa Misiri, o na rĩa ndũrĩrĩ ciothe iria itaambataga igathiĩ gũkũngũĩra Gĩathĩ kĩu gĩa Ithũnũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 39:30">Thaam 39:30</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 46:20">Ezek 46:20</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthenya ũcio-rĩ, mbugi cia mbarathi ikaandĩkwo, ICI CIAMŨRĨIRWO JEHOVA, nacio nyũngũ cia kũruga iria irĩ nyũmba ya Jehova thĩinĩ igaatuĩka ta mbakũri iria nyamũre irĩ mbere ya kĩgongona. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 31:40">Jer 31:40</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 14:6-7">Arom 14:6-7</ref></char></note>Nyũngũ o yothe ĩrĩ kũu Jerusalemu na Juda ĩkaamũrĩrwo Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe, nao arĩa othe magookaga kũruta igongona-rĩ, makooyaga nyũngũ imwe cia cio makaruga nacio. Na mũthenya ũcio-rĩ, gũtigacooka kũgĩa na mwonjorithia thĩinĩ wa nyũmba ya Jehova Mwene-Hinya-Wothe.</para>
